        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>密码学--RSA加密算法</title>
      <link href="/2020/09/21/%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81%E5%AD%A6-RSA%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/"/>
      <url>/2020/09/21/%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81%E5%AD%A6-RSA%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="0x1-加密原理"><a href="#0x1-加密原理" class="headerlink" title="0x1.加密原理"></a>0x1.加密原理</h3><p>首先选取两个不同的大素数p,q，求出：<br>$$<br>\varphi(N)=(p-1)<em>(q-1)<br>$$<br>$$<br>N=p</em>q<br>$$<br>选取一个数e，e满足0&lt;e&lt;&varphi;(N)且e和&varphi;(N)互素，把e作为加密密钥，然后根据<br>$$<br>ed\equiv 1modN<br>$$<br>求出一个d，把d作为解密密钥。<br>如果明文为m,密文为c，则<br>$$<br>c = m^e mod N<br>$$<br>$$<br>m = c^d mod N<br>$$</p><p>在使用过程中把(N,e)作为公钥，把(d)作为私钥。p,q可以丢弃，但是不可以公开。</p><h3 id="0x2-加解密用到的库"><a href="#0x2-加解密用到的库" class="headerlink" title="0x2.加解密用到的库"></a>0x2.加解密用到的库</h3><h4 id="1-gmp库-C"><a href="#1-gmp库-C" class="headerlink" title="1.gmp库(C++)"></a>1.gmp库(C++)</h4><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">mpz_t</span> b;<span class="comment">//定义一个大整数变量</span></span><br><span class="line">mpz_init_set_str(b, <span class="string">"12345678900987654321"</span>, <span class="number">10</span>);<span class="comment">//以十进制的形式把数字存储到b中</span></span><br><span class="line">mpz_sub(c,b,a);<span class="comment">//c=b-a</span></span><br><span class="line">mpz_add(c,b,a);<span class="comment">//c=a+b</span></span><br><span class="line">mpz_mul(c,b,a)<span class="comment">//c=b*a</span></span><br><span class="line">mpz_pow(c,b,a)<span class="comment">//c=b**a</span></span><br><span class="line">mpz_powm(c,m,e,n)<span class="comment">//c=m**e mod n</span></span><br><span class="line">mpz_cmp(a,b)<span class="comment">//如果a，b相等返回0，不相等返回非零值</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-python"><a href="#2-python" class="headerlink" title="2.python"></a>2.python</h3><p>后期补充</p><h3 id="常见攻击方法"><a href="#常见攻击方法" class="headerlink" title="常见攻击方法"></a>常见攻击方法</h3><p>后面补充</p><h3 id="例题"><a href="#例题" class="headerlink" title="例题"></a>例题</h3><h4 id="攻防世界Signin"><a href="#攻防世界Signin" class="headerlink" title="攻防世界Signin"></a>攻防世界Signin</h4><p>本题分析代码可以看出是把用户的输入经过变换之后又进行了一次rsa加密，最后和已知明文字符串，进行比较，判断输入是否为想要输入。<br>经过分析N=103461035900816914121390101299049044413950405173712170434161686539878160984549，在<a href="http://www.factordb.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://www.factordb.com/</a> 上进行大素数分解，分解得p=282164587459512124844245113950593348271,q=366669102002966856876605669837014229419<br>然后借用别人脚本求解出d，如下：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">p = <span class="number">366669102002966856876605669837014229419</span></span><br><span class="line">q = <span class="number">282164587459512124844245113950593348271</span></span><br><span class="line">N = <span class="number">103461035900816914121390101299049044413950405173712170434161686539878160984549</span></span><br><span class="line">c = <span class="number">0xad939ff59f6e70bcbfad406f2494993757eee98b91bc244184a377520d06fc35</span></span><br><span class="line">e = <span class="number">65537</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">ext_euclid</span><span class="params">(a, b)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    old_s,s=<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">    old_t,t=<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">    old_r,r=a,b</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> b == <span class="number">0</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, a</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span>(r!=<span class="number">0</span>):</span><br><span class="line">            q=old_r//r</span><br><span class="line">            old_r,r=r,old_r-q*r</span><br><span class="line">            old_s,s=s,old_s-q*s</span><br><span class="line">            old_t,t=t,old_t-q*t</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> old_s, old_t, old_r</span><br><span class="line">ol=(p<span class="number">-1</span>)*(q<span class="number">-1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">d=ext_euclid(ol,e)[<span class="number">1</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> d&lt;<span class="number">0</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    d+=ol</span><br><span class="line">m = pow(c, d, N)</span><br><span class="line">print(bytes.fromhex(hex(m)[<span class="number">2</span>:]))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> RSA,密码学 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
